
<head>

<style>
  .sign-google {
    background: url('https://images.theconversation.com/files/93616/original/image-20150902-6700-t2axrz.jpg?ixlib=rb-1.1.0&q=45&auto=format&w=1000&fit=clip') #f2f2f2;
    background-position: -9px -7px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: 37px 40px;
    padding-left: 42px;
  }
  
  .link{
    color: #0F52BA;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .link:hover{
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  .welcome{
  font-family: "Lucida Console", "Courier New", monospace;
  font-size: 20px;
  padding-top: 20px;
  padding-bottom: 10px;
  }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  
  <% if @current_user == nil %>

  <div class="px-4 py-5 my-5 text-center">
    <img class="d-block mx-auto mb-4" src="https://www.creativefabrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14/Meerkats-clipart-African-cute-animals-Graphics-7163564-3-580x387.jpg" alt="" width="100" height="70">
    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Welcome to Meerkat</h1>
    <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
      <p class="lead mb-4">Wanna find some partners at Columbia to do group project, have dinner, go hiking, etc. together? <br> Start from Meerkat! <br> You can select suitable partners, find interesting activities, and join various groups. <br> Meerkat is also friendly to socially awkward people. All the posts and comments will be anonymously published.</p>
      <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center">
      <a class="btn btn-primary sign-google" href="/auth/google_oauth2" role="button">Log in with Google</a>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
  
  
  <% else %>

  <div class="px-4 py-5 my-5 text-center">
    <img class="d-block mx-auto mb-4" src="https://www.creativefabrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14/Meerkats-clipart-African-cute-animals-Graphics-7163564-3-580x387.jpg" alt="" width="100" height="70">
    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Welcome to Meerkat</h1>
    <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
      <p class="lead mb-4">Wanna find some partners at Columbia to do group project, have dinner, go hiking, etc. together? <br> Start from Meerkat! <br> You can select suitable partners, find interesting activities, and join various groups. <br> Meerkat is also friendly to socially awkward people. All the posts and comments will be anonymously published.</p>
      <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 gap-3"><%= link_to "Go to Posts", posts_path, :method => :get, :class => "link"%></button>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 gap-3"><%= link_to "My Profile", profile_path, :method => :get, :class => "link"%></button>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4"><%= link_to "Log out", logout_path, :method => :delete, :class => "link"%></button>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <% end %>
  
</body>

